{"type":"article","id":17592,"title":"譚德塞嗆種族歧視,小粉紅假冒台人道歉","uid":33812,"topics":[2254,5889,161,16,5419,130],"contents":"身為台灣人真的已經受夠這種事了,幸好中國網軍英文不好<br>\n支持Tedros對恐嚇侮辱者提告，這種事在台灣也不被允許，直接指責台灣政府通融種族歧視根本沒證據，<br>\n網民應為自己的歧視發言負責，但請Tedros別把無能失職的指責當成種族歧視<br>\n況且3個月前台灣人根本不認識Tedros<br>\n________________________________________<br>\n世界衛生組織秘書長譚德塞，日前批評台灣對他人身攻擊、種族歧視，長達三個月，外交部不滿不實指控，要求譚德塞澄清道歉，不過調查局發現，有大陸網軍，從昨天下午一點多開始，在twitter假冒台灣網友，向譚德塞道歉。<br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/MbThCF5.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/MbThCF5.png\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/MbThCF5.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/3l9ypwd.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/3l9ypwd.png\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/3l9ypwd.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/h9yJPdJ.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/h9yJPdJ.png\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/h9yJPdJ.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/7ORaL8a.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/7ORaL8a.png\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/7ORaL8a.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/Nzhb1ry.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/Nzhb1ry.png\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/Nzhb1ry.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-04-11","agreeCount":5,"discussionCount":0}